description._content: Photographer: Unknown, Non-Indian Subject: George Gustav Heye (GGH), Non-Indian, 1874-1957        Nacoochee Mound Expedition (1915) Date Created: 1915 Catalog Number: P11604 Format: Albumen print Dimensions: 3.25 x 4 in.
